column2: I found it ironic that the manager's name is Sunny because his disposition is anything but
The team didnt seem like they want to be there, from the greet and the goodbye it was rushed
The Young lady on the counter was not interested in the customer and tended to want to get me out rather than ask if I was happy
The technician blocked me from getting out of my car I think he was trying to be funny but I didn't find it that funny
The service from the staff was good, but the manager  not Miguel was rude
